				</h2>
				<p class="logo-showcase-subtitle">
					The toolkit that powers my work
					<span class="tools-subtitle-divider">·</span>
					<a href="/blog/my-stack/" class="tools-subtitle-link">Read the full breakdown <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
				</p>

				<div class="logo-showcase-section">
